programme.desc: Eredivisie je najvišje rangirano klubsko nogometno tekmovanje na Nizozemskem. Liga je bila ustanovljena leta 1956. Najuspešnejši klub je amsterdamski Ajax, ki je osvojil kar 33 naslovov državnega prvaka, sledita mu PSV (24), ki je tudi aktualni prvak, in Feyenoord (15). Od leta 1965 dalje je trem omenjenim klubom uspelo osvojiti večino državnih naslovov. Izjemi sta leti 1981 ter 2009, ko so se veselili nogometaši AZ-ja iz Alkmaarja ter leto 2010, ko je naslov romal v roke Twenteja.

programme.desc: Jason Koger shares how a life-changing accident impacted his future. He describes his history with the Union, and how he hopes to inspire others. When he heads to Texas to hunt wild hogs, Jason also embraces the sounds of the Lonestar State.(n)

programme.title: The Lindsey Way
programme.desc: Follow along Ashley Lindsey's emotional journey chasing the giant whitetail, Timber 10. After misses and close encounters over the years, the story of Timber 10 opens and closes with her Mathews bow.(n)

programme.title: On The Road With Rock & Aaron
programme.desc: Rock is in Colorado trying to fill elk and mule deer tags.(n)

programme.title: Country Boys Outdoors
programme.desc: Anyone that knows Brad knows that whitetail deer hunting is in his blood. Stretching back to his youth, Brad has lived and breathed whitetail, along with the track record to prove it.(n)

programme.title: Major League Bowhunter
programme.desc: BA & B-Dank are in their backyard of northwest Oklahoma trying to get within archery range of mature river bottom whitetails. No stranger to this part of the country, B-Dank hunts in early November and BA comes in mid-December.(n)

programme.title: Guns & Gear
programme.desc: Crimson Trace introduces new tactical lights for long guns. Plus, SIG's suppressed upper receiver, Smith & Wesson's M&P M2.0 Compact variations, the SAINT family from Springfield Armory, and firearms storage from Liberty Safe.(n)

programme.title: Guns & Ammo TV
programme.desc: Elmer Keith heads up a "Who's Who" list of some of the greatest gunwriters of all time and how they made what G&A is today. Mention SOCOM and the words "courage" and "credibility" come to mind. The word is SOCOM is adopting the 6.5 Creedmoor.(n)

programme.title: Wild Outdoors
programme.desc: Wyatt Gregory and Anson Sutherland head to Saskatchewan with Steep Bank Outfitters hunting black bears.(n)

programme.title: Long Range Pursuit
programme.desc: Mike Davidson and longtime customer, Sam Cunningham, check the Alaskan forecast and things are looking good. A couple of mountain goat tags are burning holes in their pocket and things heat up fast when a billy is spotted.(n)

programme.title: Western Extreme
programme.desc: Jim Burnworth goes on several elk hunts.(n)

programme.title: West of Texas
programme.desc: Stephen's life revolves around deer. From his home base in south Texas to Mexico and beyond. His dedication to the sport of deer hunting has gifted many friendships and memories that will last a lifetime.(n)

programme.title: Into High Country
programme.desc: Jason joins his good friend, Lance Groff, hunting mule deer in the badlands of eastern Montana. Then, Lance takes his son Wyatt out for his first deer hunt ever. One thing is for sure, the apple doesn't fall far from the tree.(n)

programme.title: The Western Hunter
programme.desc: Part 1. Nate Simmons backpacks into the Colorado high-country with hopes of arrowing a mature mule deer, but the endeavor proves much more difficult than expected.(n)

programme.title: MeatEater
programme.sub-title: First Timers: Montana Mule Deer Pt.1
programme.desc: Part 1: Joe Rogan and Bryan Callen join Steve on a hunt for mule deer in Missouri.(n)

programme.title: MeatEater
programme.sub-title: First Timers: Montana Mule Deer Pt.2
programme.desc: Part 2: Joe Rogan and Bryan Callen join Steve on a hunt.(n)

programme.title: Red Rising
programme.desc: Chris Ward starts hunting in Virginia, and doesn't have much luck. A buddy invited him to hunt in Texas, and Chris was excited for the chance. Danny Calloway decides to tag along and is rewarded with a chance at a hog.(n)

programme.title: Big Deer TV *
programme.desc: A look back at another hunting season filled with ups, downs and a few curveballs.(n)
